## Common Commands

### Deployment

```bash
# Deploy application
kamal deploy

# Deploy with specific version
kamal deploy --version=v1.2.3

# Redeploy (rebuild and deploy)
kamal redeploy
```

### Application Management

```bash
# Start app
kamal app start

# Stop app
kamal app stop

# Restart app
kamal app restart

# Show app status
kamal app details

# Show app logs
kamal app logs

# Follow logs in real-time
kamal app logs --follow

# Show recent logs
kamal app logs --since 10m
```

### Server Management

```bash
# SSH into server
kamal app exec -i bash

# Run Rails console on server
kamal app exec -i 'bin/rails console'

# Run rake task
kamal app exec 'bin/rails db:migrate:status'

# Check server details
kamal server details
```

### Environment Variables

```bash
# Show environment variables
kamal env

# Push new environment variables
kamal env push
```

### Rollback

```bash
# Rollback to previous version
kamal rollback

# Rollback to specific version
kamal rollback --version=v1.2.2
```

### Cleanup

```bash
# Remove old images
kamal prune

# Remove old containers
kamal prune --containers

# Remove everything
kamal prune --all
```

